  "subject": "1.3.3 release",
  "commit_message": "1.3.3 release\n\n- replace integration-java11 base image with eclipse-temurin\n- update spring-boot (2.5.9 -> 2.5.15)\n- update spring-cloud (2020.0.4 -> 2020.0.6)\n- update commons-codec (1.17.1 -> 1.18.0)\n- update commons-lang3 (3.16.0 -> 3.17.0)\n- support prometheus metrics\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-4759\nChange-Id: I7c3b525cb13bb14c97f2cba84bb3fce242cb0f9c\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
